{"tid":2297212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支聯會無懼打壓 續辦六四集會","createTime":"2020-11-23T06:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T06:18:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"293b67fa90d8110e945f71a701bf5f36dc7af22f","tid":2297212,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:15:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/5A5EUAZMQJBDDN3AZUDJAF3QYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2F5A5EUAZMQJBDDN3AZUDJAF3QYQ%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUndOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=7c231028\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2F5A5EUAZMQJBDDN3AZUDJAF3QYQ%2F&h=8d59673f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/5A5EUAZMQJBDDN3AZUDJAF3QYQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n支聯會無懼打壓 續辦六四集會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ykreu6_8WOKfiWs6MaUDYKbvRP8=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZNZMPWPAQBB4BAOHS4VA5OR3MA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fykreu6_8WOKfiWs6MaUDYKbvRP8%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZNZMPWPAQBB4BAOHS4VA5OR3MA.jpg&h=513ac27d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■支聯會昨於銅鑼灣擺街站收集聖誕卡，聲援中港維權人士。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】支聯會早前再遭全國港澳研究會理事田飛龍撰文批評違反國安法後，昨無懼打壓繼續收集聖誕卡慰問中港維權人士。主席李卓人批評內地政治針對、「砌生豬肉」思維侵蝕香港，表明支聯會堅持五大綱領，並繼續舉辦六四集會，並已提出申請場地，強調要以真相對抗謊言。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李卓人：已申請場地<br />\n<br />\n支聯會昨於銅鑼灣擺街站，維持每年一度的收集聖誕卡行動，寄予中港維權人士，包括在囚的六四天網創辦人黃琦、香港出版人姚文田、以及天安門母親和被扣留內地的12港人等，並掛起「結束一黨專政，建設民主中國」橫額；數名警員在場戒備並拍攝現場。<br />\n<br />\n李卓人批評，田飛龍說法將內地法制思維加諸香港，「先政治上針對維權人士，搜羅證據再砌生豬肉」，強調支聯會在國安法實施時已表明不會調整綱領。對田指控支聯會挑戰中共歷史話語權，李直言：「我絕對承認，六四紀念館就係用真相對抗謊言」，重申30年來一直和平推動「結束一黨專政」等五大綱領，「30年來所做嘅𠵱家有問題，唔係我哋變咗，而係香港變咗」。李強調會堅持五大綱領、爭取民主無罪，又透露支聯會已着手籌辦來年六四集會，包括申請場地。<br />\n<br />\n常委鄧岳君指，支聯會工作不涉恐怖活動、。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n=============<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e182aa0b1e4c1daf75517eb529ef47f826aaea","tid":2297212,"uid":37990,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:16:41.000Z","msg":"唔搞點籌錢"},{"pid":"a9c415185479c371b7c21d7adfbbe0c1174382a2","tid":2297212,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:17:31.000Z","msg":"支聯會而家好尷尬<br />\n支共港共當你係反中亂港<br />\n本土當你係大中華膠<br />\n獨派當你係鄰國事務"},{"pid":"f71166c5108fe4b46495ff5df2821956d66a13b6","tid":2297212,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:18:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">左邊行 入錢 入錢 入錢 </span></span></strong>"}]}